abstract: Former Rep Jesse Jackson Jr is released from Alabama federal prison, two years after pleading guilty to misuse of campaign funds.
lead_paragraph: Former Representative Jesse Jackson Jr. left an Alabama federal prison early Thursday, two years after pleading guilty to spending $750,000 in campaign money on personal items.

headline.main: Illinois: Jesse Jackson Jr. Leaves Prison
